msgid "other more or less frequent sidebars are rather explicit: CULTURE, TIP, CAUTION, GOING FURTHER, SECURITY, and so on."
msgstr "boks lain yang jarang digunakan antara lain cenderung eksplisit: KULTUR, TIP, PERHATIAN, LEBIH LANJUT, KEAMANAN, dan seterusnya."

